reviewText:
Just Another Romantic Wrestling Comedy is the perfect film for the entire family. The film has an all star wrestling cast including greats like Don Frye, April Hunter, Joanie "Chyna" Laurer, and Ken Yasuda. Weather you're a wrestling fan or not, you will enjoy this wonderful film. It's easy to follow plot and friendly humor makes it great for people of all ages and genders.

The acting is great, the script writing was excellent, and the filming is of very high quality. Anyone who is either a wrestling fan or who is looking for a fun, family oriented comedy will love this film.
